model.name: Friday Night Funkin Pack
model.description: A Friday Night Funkin model/map pack for Beat Saber! This pack contains: notes, sabers, and 7 custom environments. All 22 songs from the OST have also been included in a seperate playlist, and have easy, hard, and expert+ so everybody can play! To install, simply drag the .zip/playlist into BMBF. PC version can be found [here](https://bobbie.dev/FNFPack). If you like this pack consider joining my [patreon](https://www.patreon.com/bobbievr)!
